text: Scott Froml (born 21 August 1987), better known by his stage name Kerser, is an Australian rapper. His best known song is "Kerser Is the Sickest". He was released a number of mixtapes and three albums since 2011. His second album No Rest For the Sickest reached #15 on the ARIA albums chart. Kerser was born in Campbelltown, Sydney, New South Wales. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1987 births Category:Australian singers Category:Australian musicians Category:Hip hop musicians Category:Living people Category:Musicians from New South Wales Category:People from Sydney
